panel-heading\">\n				<span class=\"icon-lightbulb\"></span> Tips of the day</header>\n			<div class=\"panel-body\" style=\"padding:0\">\n				<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://api.prestashop.com/partner/tipsoftheday/img/logo-avalara.png\" style=\"float:right; margin-left: 5px;\">\n				<img src=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/api/getAdviceImg/508.png\"/>\n				<p><b>What do accountants think?</b></p>\n				<p>52% of accountants would rather run a marathon than try and crack the sales tax code.</p>\n				<span class=\"text-right\" style=\"float:right\">\n					<a class=\"btn btn-default\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/get_advice_link.php?id_advice=508&url=http%3A%2F%2Faddons.prestashop.com%2Fen%2Fbilling-invoicing-prestashop-modules%2F5040-avalara-avatax.html%3Futm_source%3Dback-office%26utm_medium%3Dtipoftheday%26utm_campaign%3Dpartenariats%26utm_content%3Davalara\">More information?</a>\n				</span>\n			</div>\n		</section>\n		<section id=\"1_avalara\" class=\"panel \" style=\"display:none\">\n			<header class=\"panel-heading\">\n				<span class=\"icon-lightbulb\"></span> Tips of the day</header>\n			<div class=\"panel-body\" style=\"padding:0\">\n				<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://api.prestashop.com/partner/tipsoftheday/img/logo-avalara.png\" style=\"float:right; margin-left: 5px;\">\n				<img src=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/api/getAdviceImg/508.png\"/>\n				<p><b>Did you know there are specific tax rules for each state?</b></p>\n				<p>Clothing is exempt from Sales Tax in Pennsylvania, except for formal wear.</p>\n				<span class=\"text-right\" style=\"float:right\">\n					<a class=\"btn btn-default\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://gamification.prestashop.com/get_advice_link.php?id_advice=508&url=http%3A%2F%2Faddons.prestashop.com%2Fen%2Fbilling-invoicing-prestashop-modules%2F5040-avalara-avatax.html%3Futm_source%3Dback-office%26utm_medium%3Dtipoftheday%26utm_campaign%3Dpartenariats%26utm_content%